{"tid":1359141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「光復元朗」與「以武制暴」","createTime":"2019-07-24T05:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T06:33:42.000Z","uid":61886,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4caa5b8a806963bad56c997bda6f8cd5e9241872","tid":1359141,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:20:43.000Z","msg":"我個人理解<br />\n以武制暴即係<br />\n以武力去制止或制裁暴力、暴政、暴權或其從屬<br />\n<br />\n先利申 <br />\n本人較偏向勇武派<br />\n可起底睇<br />\n我開好多裝備等等既post<br />\n<br />\n由衝立法會、向警犬還拖、圍警署、圍中聯辦、搞TVB、圍新城市等<br />\n我都支持<br />\n因為正正係實踐緊以武制暴<br />\n對準暴政同佢既幫兇<br />\n去制裁佢地<br />\n<br />\n727光復元朗<br />\n去係一定要去<br />\n因為唔可以屈服於黑社會之下<br />\n我地要夠多人去<br />\n話比佢地聽 黑社會我地都唔驚<br />\n<br />\n有黑社會搞鳩我地<br />\n我地100%還拖<br />\n只要唔打死人就得<br />\n<br />\n但要緊記<br />\n無差別既暴力<br />\n例如拆祠堂等<br />\n對準唔到黑社會既話<br />\n就會好似白衫既行為一樣<br />\n<br />\n點都好<br />\n義士果日做左咩都好<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但都記得<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不被捕 不流血</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5a469a5a4a9171efd90abec44332189bdb60b42d","tid":1359141,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:21:30.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論<br />\n如有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faee9f150e60df5111426a30afa5ec5637fa936e","tid":1359141,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4351fcce16ab28f334cb6600466d90483e980dd2","tid":1359141,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:22:16.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n必睇前導發言<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVEUhAVki0DA&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=439b6ce9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA</a><br />\n<br />\n森美教你應付滿口歪理嘅人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KCdy68i7cl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKCdy68i7cl0&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=20ef4627\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KCdy68i7cl0</a>"},{"pid":"9c797ef740451dde1d83a403afc5f27a7f793de3","tid":1359141,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:22:44.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"31957282ff0ed781fac099c49d9047856d80a1f1","tid":1359141,"uid":74572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:23:25.000Z","msg":"借位 順手幫推 麻煩幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【越洋幫拖】喺美國嘅香港人想收集警暴證據交畀美國警察同議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1358473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1358473</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d885ed2d87a6ad177824dabeb300b0dbef6c38f2","tid":1359141,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:23:29.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"2fbca31a618419b01fc60d2c1b10dc44b6e6d263","tid":1359141,"uid":191989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58fa495047bdb040f7525019783e274ab5d2005e","tid":1359141,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"都話唔係光復<br />\n係反警黑合作<br />\n<br />\n光復元朗變左 元朗村民守村 vs 外來者入元朗"},{"pid":"bb70aaad75d4c6339ef2b2df01b626e5bc59f029","tid":1359141,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"我都唔明點解有咁多人到而家都未醒，一心淨係想報仇，佢地知唔知行錯一步郁咗手先真係要成個運動部葬架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkg